Read this proposal in full;

Why İncrease AUTO CAKE POOL %APY

*  The end goal of İncreasing AUTO CAKE POOL %APY is to make PancakeSwap attractive. That means more CAKE’s Staked on PancakeSwap and More CAKE’s be Bought. Hight %APY is important for the future of PancakeSwap *



❌ No change:

# ➕ 1 CAKE per block İncrease to AUTO CAKE POOL rewards:  #

⚠️  Please note⚠️ 

One option must have a majority of 50%+ at the end snapshot in order to win the vote and be executed. If none of the options get over 50% of the vote, we'll create a new proposal.
